Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:46.56,IN-EP12-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I feel like I’m losing hope
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:49.01,IN-EP12-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}In my body and my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:55.64,IN-EP12-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}And the sky, it looks so ominous
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:59.41,IN-EP12-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}And as time comes to a halt
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:02.06,IN-EP12-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}Silence starts to overflow
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:07.96,IN-EP12-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}My cries are inconspicuous
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:14.91,IN-EP12-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}Tell me God, are you punishing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:21.45,IN-EP12-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}Is this the price I’m paying for my past mistakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:27.86,IN-EP12-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}This is my redemption song
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:33.77,IN-EP12-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I need you more than ever right now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:37.56,IN-EP12-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}Can you hear me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:40.84,IN-EP12-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}Cause we’re going to shout it loud
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:44.06,IN-EP12-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}Even if our word seem meaningless
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:50.20,IN-EP12-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}It’s like I’m carrying the weight of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:53.88,IN-EP12-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I wish that someway, somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:57.12,IN-EP12-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}That I can save every one of us
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:12:02.80,IN-EP12-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}But the truth is that I’m only one girl
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:12.54,IN-EP12-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}Maybe if I keep believing my dreams will come to life
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:18.03,IN-EP12-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}Come to life…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:46.56,IN-EP12-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我感到希冀之光日趋渺茫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:49.01,IN-EP12-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}在身体与灵魂深处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:55.64,IN-EP12-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}不祥笼罩着天空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:59.41,IN-EP12-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}时间静止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:02.06,IN-EP12-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}死寂开始蔓延
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:07.96,IN-EP12-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我的号哭是如此微弱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:14.91,IN-EP12-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}告诉我，上帝，你是否在惩罚我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:21.45,IN-EP12-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}这就是我要为旧日过错付出的代价吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:27.86,IN-EP12-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}这是我的救赎之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:33.77,IN-EP12-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}现在我比任何时候都更需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:37.56,IN-EP12-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}你能否听到我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:40.84,IN-EP12-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}正因如此，我们如今要竭力呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:44.06,IN-EP12-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}哪怕我们的话语毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:50.20,IN-EP12-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}就像是承受着整个世界的重量一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:53.88,IN-EP12-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我希望某时，以某种方式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:57.12,IN-EP12-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我可以拯救所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:12:02.80,IN-EP12-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}但我 仅是孤身一人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:12.54,IN-EP12-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}如果我坚持相信我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:18.03,IN-EP12-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}也许它就会变成现实…
